[*] --> Active
Active --> Shipped : submit
Active : entry / log interest
Shipped --> Closed : cancel
Closed --> Draft : cancel
Closed : entry / log interest
Draft --> Pending : reject
Pending --> Approved : update
Pending : entry / log interest
Active --> Approved : revert
Approved --> [*]
